# Pipeline Overview

Pipeline menggunakan pendekatan stepped workflow.

Setiap script:

* memiliki single responsibility
* memiliki input dan output yang jelas
* menghasilkan artifact `.rds`
* dapat di-rerun secara independen

---

# Pipeline Rules

## Naming Convention

Semua script menggunakan format:

```text id="8zaxf7"
00_
01_
02_
xx_
```

Contoh:

```text id="lk7i3q"
00_config.R
01_load_merge.R
09_train_logistic.R
```

---

## Script Rules

Setiap file wajib memiliki header:

```r id="gq0i6h"
# ==============================================================================
# filename.R
# Script Description
# ==============================================================================
```

---

## Console Output Rules

Gunakan:

* `message()`
* `print()`

Hindari:

* excessive `cat()`
* unnecessary console spam

---

## Code Quality Rules

### Wajib

* explicit pipeline
* clean variable naming
* avoid duplicated logic
* avoid magic number
* avoid hidden dependency
* consistent indentation
* stable artifact naming

### Hindari

* namespace berlebihan
* separator comment berlebihan
* mutate berulang tanpa kebutuhan
* nested pipe yang terlalu panjang

