# Recommended Workflow

## First Run

Run sequentially:

```text id="5yy9na"
00 → 01 → 02 → 03 → 04 → 05 → 06 → 08 → 09a → 09
```

---

## Experiment Workflow

If only model changes:

```text id="fh4eqe"
09 → 10 → 11 → 12
```

No need rerun preprocessing.

---

## Feature Engineering Workflow

If feature selection changes:

```text id="pjlwm1"
08 → 09a → 09 → 10 → 11 → 12
```

---

# Best Practices

## DO

* rerun only impacted steps
* keep artifact naming stable
* validate every output
* use clear dependency chain
* print concise metrics only

---

## DON'T

* rename artifact randomly
* overwrite unrelated artifact
* mix preprocessing + modeling
* add unnecessary console logs
* create hidden dependency between scripts

